		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_BLACKDEATH_SCENARIO_NAME">
			<Text>The Black Death</Text>
		<Replace>
		<Replace Language='en_US' Tag="LOC_LOADING_INFO_BLACKDEATH_SCENARIO">
			<Text>The Black Death ravaged Europe and Western Asia in the mid-14th century, killing a greater share of the population than any other event in world history. The pandemic killed millions, ruined economies, upended political dynasties and transformed the face of the Western world.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Your task is to lead your nation through the calamity: keep your population alive, your economy strong, and your faith unshaken amidst a world of terror and desperation.</Text>
		<Replace>
